  "templateName": "MacOSGlassTransactionDashboardTemplate",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "面向数字化交易中台、跨境收单、渠道流量、API 节点状态和企业经营复盘的 macOS 玻璃态交互数据大屏。",
  "pageTypes": [
    "dashboard",
